But then, wave equations.

2674
01:54:08,306 --> 01:54:09,806
Wave equations because we're going to

2675
01:54:09,806 --> 01:54:11,306
want to study electricity and magnetism.

2676
01:54:11,306 --> 01:54:12,306
We're going to study light.

2677
01:54:12,306 --> 01:54:15,306
We're going to study light, light waves, and so forth.

